## DESCRIPTION
##  Reduce 3x5 to row echelon form
##   Change size in code by editing variables at start
## ENDDESCRIPTION

## DBsubject(Linear algebra)
## DBchapter(Matrices)
## DBsection(Echelon form)
## Institution(METU-NCC)
